QueryResult.text: SELECT PRJ_RESOURCES.PRUID, PRJ_RESOURCES.PRID, PRJ_RESOURCES.PRID AS PRRESOURCEID, PRJ_RESOURCES.PRPRIMARYROLEID AS PRROLEID, PRJ_RESOURCES.LAST_UPDATED_BY PRMODBY, PRJ_RESOURCES.LAST_UPDATED_DATE PRMODTIME, '1' AS PRISPRIMARY, '1.0' AS PRPROFICIENCY FROM PRJ_RESOURCES WHERE PRJ_RESOURCES.PRPRIMARYROLEID IS NOT NULL
